## System Operation

### 1. Initial Setup

```
1. Launch Playwright
2. Launch Chromium
3. Apply Stealth
4. Set HTTP headers
5. Login to DeepSeek
6. Send initial message
```

### 2. Normal Chat Mode

```
1. User sends message
2. Message sent to DeepSeek
3. Wait for response
4. Display response
5. Repeat
```

### 3. Linux Automation Mode

```
1. User enters task
2. Send systematic message
3. Receive command from model
4. Execute command
5. Send output to model
6. Receive next command
7. Repeat until completion
8. Receive "--PK--PK--PK--" signal
9. End
```

