## Installation and Usage

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.10 or higher
- Chromium browser
- Linux or WSL (for automation mode)

### Installation Steps

```bash
# 1. Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/dal.git
cd dal

# 2. Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# 3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 4. Install Chromium
playwright install chromium

# 5. Configure login credentials
# Edit creds.py or use environment variables

# 6. Run program
python main.py
```

### Execution Arguments

```bash
# Normal mode
python main.py

# Linux mode (with password)
python main.py --use 2 --sudo-password YOUR_PASSWORD
```

