## Improvement Areas

### Security

| Priority | Item | Description |
|----------|------|-------------|
| High | Remove password from code | Use environment variables |
| High | Use `.env` | Store sensitive information |
| High | Remove `creds.py` | Prevent information exposure |
| Medium | Encrypt information | Use Keyring |
| Medium | Login validation | Check password strength |

### Code Quality

| Priority | Item | Description |
|----------|------|-------------|
| High | Docstrings | Add descriptions to functions |
| High | Type Hints | Add data types |
| High | Fix `moduals` spelling | `modules` |
| Medium | Use `logging` | Replace print |
| Medium | Exception Handling | Improve error handling |
| Medium | File separation | Split `chatWithModel.py` |

### Performance

| Priority | Item | Description |
|----------|------|-------------|
| High | Improve `GetLastResponse` | Use `wait_for_function()` |
| Medium | Configurable timeout | Set wait time |
| Medium | Improve `Loginer.py` | Better error handling |
| Medium | Retry logic | Retry failed requests |

### Structure

| Priority | Item | Description |
|----------|------|-------------|
| High | Configuration File | YAML/JSON instead of hardcoded values |
| High | CLI Arguments | Use `argparse` |
| Medium | `__init__.py` | Convert to package |
| Medium | `setup.py` | Easy installation |

